ion\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"id\": \"f-repl\", \"text\": \"aside repl gives deterministic JS browser automation (openTab, screenshots, downloads)\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"id\": \"f-mcp-stdio\", \"text\": \"aside mcp runs an MCP server over stdio: command 'aside', args ['mcp']; mcp.json registration documented\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"id\": \"f-auth-tiers\", \"text\": \"Three provider tiers: Aside (built-in, needs sign-in), Subscription (OAuth), API (BYO key)\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"id\": \"f-permissions\", \"text\": \"Permission modes Read-only/Guard(default)/Full-access; layered agent+session rules; Allow/Ask/Deny\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"id\": \"f-password-boundary\", \"text\": \"Password autofill exists but raw values stay hidden from the agent\", \"run\": 1}\n  ],\n  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n    {\"approach\": \"npm install -g aside\", \"reason\": \"Documented installer is a curl script, not npm\", \"evidence\": \"https://docs.aside.com/help/developers\", \"iteration\": 1}\n  ],\n  \"promotedIdeas\": [\n    {\"id\": \"idea-runtime-discovery\", \"text\": \"MCP tool inventory for aside mcp is not in public docs; discover at runtime via Code Mode call_tool_chain / list_tools\", \"observationCount\": 1, \"firstObservedRun\": 1}\n  ],\n  \"rejectedPatterns\": [],\n  \"blockedStopHistory\": []\n}"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/008-mcp-aside/001-research/research/lineages/glm/findings-registry.json\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/008-mcp-aside/001-research/research/lineages/glm/findings-registry.json\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/008-mcp-aside/001-research/research/lineages/glm/findings-registry.json\n@@ -1,18 +1,34 @@\n {\n 